{"tha-ap180:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap180:0.2":"Kumudavagga ","tha-ap180:0.3":"Manipujakattheraapadana ","tha-ap180:1.1":"“Orena himavantassa, ","tha-ap180:1.2":"nadika sampavattatha; ","tha-ap180:1.3":"Tassa canupakhettamhi, ","tha-ap180:1.4":"sayambhu vasate tada. ","tha-ap180:2.1":"Manim paggayha pallankam, ","tha-ap180:2.2":"sadhucittam manoramam; ","tha-ap180:2.3":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap180:2.4":"buddhassa abhiropayim. ","tha-ap180:3.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap180:3.2":"yam manim abhiropayim; ","tha-ap180:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap180:3.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap180:4.1":"Ito ca dvadase kappe, ","tha-ap180:4.2":"sataramsisanamaka; ","tha-ap180:4.3":"Attha te asum rajano, ","tha-ap180:4.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap180:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap180:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap180:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap180:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma manipujako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap180:7.1":"Manipujakattherassapadanam atthamam. "}